WEBVTT

1f68ac83-061e-41af-9521-90e775deface
00:00:06.350 --> 00:00:11.720
(Shooting Star, the colorful harmony of light.)

6a3a2c41-593c-4a98-97d1-461588928b21
00:00:12.180 --> 00:00:15.020
(Catch Catch, Lighting Star, Shooting Star!)

cd1621c8-0161-4734-9d5f-be4248eb6724
00:00:15.220 --> 00:00:18.980
(Catch Catch, Teenieping!)

26afc9a5-0f63-41f4-b6bd-23d6b00fa1ea
00:00:19.420 --> 00:00:22.020
(Shalalala... Shalalala...)

6ebc5ca6-5539-4b2a-b789-5871324f9a8f
00:00:22.560 --> 00:00:25.260
(Shooting Star Teenieping!)

77a222c9-c92c-46ad-b35d-deeb41d0c10d
00:00:25.560 --> 00:00:28.160
(Heartsping of love, Shimmerping of healing,)

555d5bc4-7f0a-4d20-9cf6-9b2139ea7690
00:00:28.460 --> 00:00:31.430
(Sparkleping of wishes, Twinkleping of brightness.)

a603b0a2-df9d-4a32-8d34-7923f8dee65d
00:00:31.780 --> 00:00:34.540
(Shalala... Shalala...)

ed674bbb-4e65-49e7-b065-d6816dd0bfc5
00:00:34.620 --> 00:00:37.750
(Show me your mysterious magic! Hachu!)

d5ecbead-12e9-4221-b1ca-5e9b2c2de133
00:00:40.400 --> 00:00:45.330
(Shooting Star, the colorful harmony of light.)

151dc4f6-7049-4686-bcfa-6afa3b07cb1d
00:00:45.600 --> 00:00:48.510
(Catch Catch, Lighting Star, Shooting Star!)

8a07c98b-3e78-4625-ba3f-be80aef771de
00:00:48.710 --> 00:00:52.680
(Catch Catch, Teenieping!)

dba7b317-b615-41e7-a899-5bc2e975165b
00:00:52.920 --> 00:00:57.190
(Shooting Star Teenieping!)

6fdb4a74-416b-4a9b-86dc-c8fa6bc33eeb
00:01:04.570 --> 00:01:06.140
Sing with Ruruping!

266a1b20-a866-46a7-bdb9-7c4d779dba9a
00:01:11.751 --> 00:01:15.151
(I will sing a song for you.)

61f5cc6d-6df6-46d3-a583-7626db07a52d
00:01:16.141 --> 00:01:19.581
(Even the stars up there follow me.)

27c1cfc8-035b-445c-ac83-b26eef483f89
00:01:21.151 --> 00:01:28.241
(It's a magic that makes us all happy, rurururu.)

3a1dc399-ca87-43d1-8301-9e3c1975e13e
00:01:29.581 --> 00:01:33.451
(The twinkling stars and the Milky Way,)

b08600cb-55e7-48ff-be29-79bfd833914a
00:01:34.921 --> 00:01:38.291
(they all follow me.)

79a6c13e-e31d-4dff-ab0d-bcbd74044bdf
00:01:41.111 --> 00:01:44.931
(Sing a sing a song, sing me a song.)

4c3372ae-6f28-4c5c-84b9-68440002d81a
00:01:45.891 --> 00:01:49.441
(A melody that brightens my heart.)

65418f7d-3bdd-4f91-97e9-4d114ea75f78
00:01:50.141 --> 00:01:54.021
(Sing a sing a song, for you, I)

13a5fdac-d3b9-435d-82a5-59d14b780e0c
00:01:54.911 --> 00:01:58.211
(will become a singing star.)

6c54af52-dc3b-4367-82db-415a4bdad507
00:02:14.341 --> 00:02:18.061
Thank you so much for being the audience for my song, ruru!

2e41159f-fabf-4e9d-8dab-2e9e20e0ce75
00:02:19.081 --> 00:02:20.611
Well then, goodbye everyone!

89bba80c-1152-4527-9df8-d0c14b1f163b
00:02:33.279 --> 00:02:34.589
Wow, you're good, Romi!

205d09cc-f4c0-4c65-9af5-8eb707a01318
00:02:35.639 --> 00:02:38.569
No, it's because Sara's guitar is so good.

39bc226b-f7dc-4e4c-b361-17b4c85ba027
00:02:39.999 --> 00:02:43.799
What's the use if the guitar is good? Your playing skills are still the same.

00e4580b-79f3-4ae1-91a4-0c47e423d307
00:02:44.759 --> 00:02:46.339
I really can't stand to listen.

1ba9e556-dae1-4cea-9517-85044dfb6408
00:02:47.339 --> 00:02:50.079
Don't pick a fight. If you're jealous, just say so.

34bbf3cf-f989-481b-95bd-e78d1dbb68d4
00:02:50.609 --> 00:02:51.819
Everyone, just a moment!

f5fcdffc-f64c-4301-96ae-fe5590789771
00:02:53.649 --> 00:02:59.789
In two weeks, there will be a street charity concert in the town square. If you participate, you'll get a full year's worth of volunteer credits.

af7846fc-bdb1-4cdd-8f3a-8adcb02fc6d1
00:03:00.329 --> 00:03:02.819
Anyone who wants to participate can sign up with Ms. Dane.

9aead981-e442-4e45-820a-9501062ceb5a
00:03:03.629 --> 00:03:04.589
A street concert?

ac363cdd-40a1-4ea0-b2c3-5049bd3d2eea
00:03:05.449 --> 00:03:07.139
Singing and playing the guitar on the street.

111e282d-4a99-4882-97b5-8ae5fc7a3ace
00:03:07.829 --> 00:03:09.439
I'm short on volunteer credits.

6be476e6-7e39-431f-9baa-763bdd110da3
00:03:10.429 --> 00:03:16.149
What's this about a street concert? Huh? Ooh... I just had a great idea.

dafd6456-da95-47c7-bead-53b707ce880e
00:03:19.728 --> 00:03:26.798
Alright, that's all for today's class. Oh, I've already signed you up for the charity concert, so don't worry and do your best, Romi.

15dc8995-d06c-43a9-8c07-088e2bc5ad8d
00:03:27.568 --> 00:03:30.018
What? Me?

e762c035-0524-4c3c-a8df-9c4cccf1ffa9
00:03:31.428 --> 00:03:35.038
Yes. You said you were shy and asked Lena to sign you up, didn't you?

16badb12-73bf-4b8b-b8c6-ce89a972405c
00:03:35.548 --> 00:03:36.988
Well then, see you all tomorrow.

78e2f818-c73e-4cb0-9951-da9fb252df19
00:03:37.538 --> 00:03:39.998
Uh, Teacher, wait a minute, Teacher!

30651ea4-2334-41cd-a816-96e83c914d87
00:03:40.488 --> 00:03:42.228
Romi, are you really going to perform?

de8c8d6c-ae57-421f-8d71-fb1bdae63778
00:03:45.718 --> 00:03:46.618
Heartsping...

df2684b7-9368-411c-89b7-da3e54f5c6da
00:03:51.849 --> 00:03:54.389
Hmm... He looks kind of tired just sitting there.

987ea76d-3acd-4798-b18b-a9ef4bf090e7
00:03:55.409 --> 00:03:58.339
I'll soothe your fatigue, ruru.

ecf726ed-538e-4287-92e1-2ef37a0fea8a
00:04:02.269 --> 00:04:03.549
A bite! I got one!

0c4d44c5-56a8-4dca-b77d-0620b8190c32
00:04:04.609 --> 00:04:05.789
Three, two, one.

8c3cb910-7cbe-4a93-900f-3675574b26f2
00:04:06.159 --> 00:04:09.439
(I will sing a song for you.)

58833d0c-5623-4a53-b6d5-acec61d39923
00:04:10.519 --> 00:04:13.919
(Even the stars up there follow me.)

f9f40cd9-9459-40eb-816d-9588b30a085f
00:04:20.309 --> 00:04:21.829
Ah, drat! I lost it!

c2f88deb-d066-45f5-a27c-ffa3f85b945c
00:04:22.289 --> 00:04:23.519
I almost had it!

c897caa0-c37f-4ff8-97fe-cc08d5b07935
00:04:23.959 --> 00:04:25.689
I can't concentrate on fishing!

0d8a8d33-c2fa-4750-a469-fcd192097e69
00:04:26.309 --> 00:04:27.919
I thought I'd catch something today!

1d98f836-3f59-4100-aa46-b68f3d19fa03
00:04:31.649 --> 00:04:33.209
Hmph... I got away, ruru...

eb87643f-8a36-4c8b-9bb9-d0c4475811cd
00:04:34.509 --> 00:04:36.569
Was the tuning wrong, ruru?

116b72f0-92e7-4a91-b595-6298b2c8e1db
00:04:38.254 --> 00:04:39.954
It was Lena's doing after all, Heartsping.

1f8b9e71-f270-473b-9458-d3978d8532b3
00:04:40.454 --> 00:04:42.494
Anyway, do you think you can do it, Romi?

47a82f38-dcc8-432f-ac15-a2f74c79ba3f
00:04:43.684 --> 00:04:44.644
I don't know...

f65e41f7-3d85-43d0-9eda-e595b22b61d1
00:04:45.304 --> 00:04:48.334
All the kids are looking forward to it, so I can't just cancel.

d25131f8-64e0-43be-b026-25c123bc53cf
00:04:49.254 --> 00:04:51.354
Ah! What am I going to do!

3d4d459b-208b-4519-b45a-e78c8ca25e1e
00:04:52.484 --> 00:04:54.714
There's no one to even teach me guitar.

48cd431a-abd5-4edb-b9a0-dbe64202a900
00:04:57.654 --> 00:04:59.394
Huh? It's the Teenieping alarm, chu!

b3a4c29b-874a-43a6-9777-712625a88ed9
00:05:02.284 --> 00:05:04.094
This familiar melody... Shimmerping?

ed9d2bc5-31af-45bd-8ed0-1c19132365b2
00:05:13.624 --> 00:05:14.654
Ah, Ruruping!

239881c9-f3e0-4989-98a5-a3dc469122a0
00:05:15.344 --> 00:05:20.154
She's a Star Teenieping who used to sing and play guitar for the stars in the village, Shimmerping.

daae092c-f05e-4aa3-b864-4af16b997853
00:05:21.234 --> 00:05:25.594
She's super, super kind. You should be able to catch her without much trouble, Sparkleping.

9a7ba21e-635e-4083-9d38-343fb9e3b5ec
00:05:26.154 --> 00:05:28.464
Let's hurry and transform before she finds us, Sparkleping!

4ee78d7b-8da9-4f87-8e8c-b58a1369ffaf
00:05:28.694 --> 00:05:29.354
Okay!

f77ebbc6-5b54-4e1b-84e3-3f48d3c99455
00:05:38.544 --> 00:05:39.464
Now, Twinkleping!

a2a9c6c8-bd41-4f54-94cc-181cb6b33339
00:05:39.694 --> 00:05:40.404
Got it!

87d24497-7e8e-4fa5-9567-cc0bf7c6d3ab
00:05:40.754 --> 00:05:42.144
Piripiri Catchring!

cb8ed87f-98d3-4b11-ae5a-fd8c8f4e2fb5
00:05:42.664 --> 00:05:44.254
Shararang!

30ea9040-4d96-4e39-836f-63b72389a0cc
00:05:45.504 --> 00:05:46.994
Into the Star Cube!

22905b64-0e4a-4424-be79-f86ace125ebe
00:05:55.274 --> 00:05:57.694
Star Teenieping, Ruruping, catch!

d66985f0-9308-46ab-b150-959efec83883
00:05:58.604 --> 00:06:01.764
Ugh, where is this, ruru?

d9d87531-f524-4f1b-bb3d-6fda2aa1ddb7
00:06:06.565 --> 00:06:07.695
Hello, Ruruping.

9b95e4a5-a344-45b8-8164-82080a71de04
00:06:08.385 --> 00:06:10.045
Sorry for catching you so suddenly.

48984712-0f19-4074-b26a-b8faa0d08f81
00:06:10.825 --> 00:06:12.335
You... who are you?

9a912576-548a-46f7-bbc8-9f83ca11c8ee
00:06:13.165 --> 00:06:19.675
I'm a princess from the Emotion Kingdom, and I'm catching Star Teeniepings to restore the Star Village.

790e1085-f7a3-4811-bfca-dd93b532def0
00:06:20.195 --> 00:06:20.915
Ruruping!

a8ceefb9-7017-494c-9a97-5793409132fb
00:06:21.265 --> 00:06:22.755
Long time no see, Sparkleping!

c2e2f95d-d712-4955-ac9e-07fd113a624c
00:06:23.515 --> 00:06:24.235
Hello!

059b4bf1-15b9-4a20-89e0-0281c4a48cc7
00:06:24.875 --> 00:06:28.185
Oh my, everyone! Ruru!

4c8c84ba-7455-4583-80bc-25f286ca9ae3
00:06:30.826 --> 00:06:31.976
Ah... I'm so tired...

d50e70ba-fa3f-4ca8-9312-81f1cc55a1df
00:06:33.826 --> 00:06:35.346
What's that guitar sound, ruru?

63085b7a-a2d4-48f3-ab40-932f84cbae42
00:06:35.986 --> 00:06:39.516
Hmm... the next chord is...

5e42f1e0-1a6f-4b7f-98b5-3f7fdf9a8538
00:06:42.186 --> 00:06:43.796
You're practicing so hard, ruru.

ae7f171c-227c-4d73-b809-d3784eb388d1
00:06:44.826 --> 00:06:46.506
Huh, Ruruping? What's up?

714dc196-ce21-4399-9066-43b3067be9e5
00:06:48.336 --> 00:06:51.526
Yeah, I heard a beautiful guitar sound coming from somewhere, ruru.

4d811448-db30-4f9d-b99a-f90d6801942e
00:06:53.306 --> 00:06:55.336
No, it's not beautiful at all.

84a59307-2307-4b64-9c04-575e369fcf48
00:06:55.986 --> 00:07:01.306
The street concert is just two weeks away, and at this rate, I'm just going to embarrass myself.

8321e412-825e-40c0-8e4a-a5f1a80f3752
00:07:02.166 --> 00:07:03.886
Don't worry too much, ruru.

0b1c6775-66a3-4f4d-940c-67eebcac03cf
00:07:04.386 --> 00:07:05.906
Even I make mistakes sometimes.

3de36ef2-1722-4be7-aa14-380609b5283b
00:07:06.516 --> 00:07:09.916
I'll help you! When it comes to performances, leave it to me.

b1a629dd-b664-48e3-b832-d926f4de2476
00:07:10.666 --> 00:07:12.116
What? Really?

d33b7694-b2c7-48c0-b76d-7cf8e54a0a96
00:07:12.576 --> 00:07:14.936
Thank you, Ruruping! You're my lifesaver!

e722b294-eefe-4ec1-b1ce-78e823be55a4
00:07:15.536 --> 00:07:19.466
I'm sorry, but you have to solve this with your own power, not with magic.

a2b15734-d57d-4538-890c-4201b6cdd188
00:07:20.256 --> 00:07:23.236
The audience can tell better if you're sincere or not.

eaed90a6-f5a9-4701-a00e-1d4468c29dc8
00:07:24.386 --> 00:07:26.546
Oh, that's kind of disappointing.

cff5838d-5a67-4233-a625-a6b73054d101
00:07:28.146 --> 00:07:29.136
Ah, I get it.

f5972735-397d-45c0-b5a5-fdc2273af524
00:07:30.346 --> 00:07:31.786
So, what should I do first?

c0f2ff48-2692-4fb9-880f-49d01b30bbbb
00:07:32.616 --> 00:07:35.916
Hmm... what song do you want to sing?

b119c87f-8a17-434b-ba84-76f6cc1ab3d8
00:07:36.656 --> 00:07:38.936
Huh? Uh...

cd7ec503-8ca9-4d67-8f38-9327845daeec
00:07:43.204 --> 00:07:47.374
It looks just like the twinkling sky from our village, doesn't it, Twinkleping?

a1dc69dd-e668-498e-a908-c0ad43f96170
00:07:48.064 --> 00:07:51.684
Still, the stars in our village are bigger and prettier, Sparkleping.

add22b4d-a0bd-4213-9bec-b2dedab75a62
00:07:53.154 --> 00:07:56.554
I want to go back soon and see the stars in our village too, Shimmerping.

fc6241a4-d174-4d30-900e-a955ae690360
00:07:57.254 --> 00:07:58.744
Me too, Twinkleping.

e8f7adad-d9ac-4a2e-9f9a-af34c6b62dbc
00:08:00.674 --> 00:08:02.104
Me too, Sparkleping.

088d9080-e981-448a-9bdb-03610e65236c
00:08:07.414 --> 00:08:11.754
Ruruping, I want to sing a song that gives you strength.

14ba0c10-e6e4-4ae8-9065-9dca6c8c3038
00:08:12.244 --> 00:08:13.914
Huh? For us?

3d58d2c5-0abc-4049-9781-d214a31cc505
00:08:14.544 --> 00:08:20.574
Yes. I saw Shimmerping, Sparkleping, and Twinkleping missing their home while looking at the sky every night.

802840f5-6ad9-49be-95d6-9b4255df2ab0
00:08:21.164 --> 00:08:26.694
I don't know when it'll be, but until we can go back, I want to tell you all to stay strong together.

cd96b67a-6843-4791-9b24-084721b56e10
00:08:27.284 --> 00:08:29.354
That's so touching, ruru!

856344ad-e53b-4312-8380-63a665336f9c
00:08:29.744 --> 00:08:34.754
Hmm... In that case, shall we start our special training, ruru?

662a062a-5d29-4192-ae18-b8d881f774b6
00:08:35.484 --> 00:08:36.934
Special training?

e1101e95-b272-43f5-a914-8472e44d3309
00:10:07.721 --> 00:10:08.821
Isn't that Romi?

91de7f62-3264-4f21-849f-62755201d275
00:10:08.971 --> 00:10:10.871
She should've run away before embarrassing herself.

92a44999-7051-409c-8838-2699021ab1f2
00:10:10.971 --> 00:10:12.631
How much could she have practiced in two weeks?

09a4b103-eb86-4a03-a719-68a46306de2e
00:10:13.151 --> 00:10:14.521
Look how unconfident she is.

b31eb914-7c1c-45bb-9f56-2e843546df52
00:10:14.671 --> 00:10:16.481
You guys just wait and see.

b9bd5103-6b02-482d-a471-f6792fa4f421
00:10:20.841 --> 00:10:22.561
You can do it, Romi!

6d5a5e71-4b66-4f85-8180-395bd4c9838d
00:10:24.961 --> 00:10:26.461
Why am I so nervous?

d19f944d-36b1-45e8-856f-5430773e0a3c
00:10:27.501 --> 00:10:29.111
Romi, come closer.

53f5407d-2e21-4768-9a70-7f16635f4be4
00:10:32.551 --> 00:10:33.221
Huh?

2db9a73d-f1b0-4ac4-b7de-5e5942e91dab
00:10:34.191 --> 00:10:38.901
I've shared my confidence with you, so you don't have to worry anymore.

26789935-3278-4f09-8fba-a153ea749d2d
00:10:39.461 --> 00:10:41.971
Just do it like you practiced. Got it, ruru?

75e36e0a-368c-4b69-b04d-50f4362f24ce
00:10:42.661 --> 00:10:43.371
Okay.

d214ab30-4075-48a5-8c48-16aa98815568
00:10:49.880 --> 00:10:53.180
(I will sing a song for you.)

27930348-a602-4469-8ed8-4bb14584c874
00:10:54.400 --> 00:10:57.940
(Even the stars up there follow me.)

e33e768f-d13a-4be4-8d21-a898149a88e8
00:10:58.590 --> 00:11:04.910
(It's a magic that makes us all happy, rurururu.)

701210ab-f3da-4d87-a1ca-c97bc8bf456c
00:11:08.120 --> 00:11:12.180
(The twinkling stars and the Milky Way,)

6e768cc4-8488-426c-9078-c2e8dd78ad5a
00:11:13.560 --> 00:11:16.790
(they all follow me.)

e8746660-e85c-45bc-a4f5-5bb7f4cbcba0
00:11:19.460 --> 00:11:23.080
(Sing a, sing a song. Sing me a song.)

38f2a9ba-5df9-41a2-b616-c50cec99d54d
00:11:24.010 --> 00:11:27.810
(A melody that brightens my heart.)

df1216be-00d3-4a9e-b4f6-d2c0a514a375
00:11:28.480 --> 00:11:32.480
(Sing a, sing a song. For you, I)

77e1ae10-a2d9-430e-8c4d-0917c3365448
00:11:33.290 --> 00:11:36.560
(will become a singing star.)

22d3088e-bbd2-42fb-910d-51e6b50444ef
00:11:37.330 --> 00:11:39.790
Tch, making a fuss over something like this.

6c53496a-fe3b-45e2-a2d3-c8fcd6e4da75
00:11:40.750 --> 00:11:41.870
Let's go, everyone.

ed5cd711-1b02-4ebe-8a13-8945d8222440
00:11:42.500 --> 00:11:42.870
Huh?

1636d050-fbf2-4677-bba8-e1480b9a49a6
00:11:55.670 --> 00:11:58.980
(As long as we're together, we're not lonely.)

bfdbb1bf-f2e0-43df-918e-f27b3333129d
00:12:00.270 --> 00:12:02.820
(Take my hand.)

a3a36923-865e-48de-b289-7f8af9791a8a
00:12:07.410 --> 00:12:09.130
(Sing a, sing a song.)

6b9597f7-3512-4595-a120-06128d52b88b
00:12:12.390 --> 00:12:15.540
(A melody that makes us all one.)

229800d2-9375-4cce-b670-5a0fd5bf27cc
00:12:16.920 --> 00:12:18.840
(Sing a, sing a song.)

adbf1563-9011-4487-8a0f-d3193fba3428
00:12:21.080 --> 00:12:21.900
(By your side,)

